quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  38,62,"Ka b…õ (toondannim‚Äô maa) yőĶli: ‚ÄúBo n-leei ch…õ ka ti bi nyari ninvu…£u shőĶba ti ni daa kaandi pahiri ninvu…£ub…õri puuni la?‚ÄĚ"
  38,63,"‚ÄúDini b…ĒŇč…Ē, ti daa kuli maandi ba la ansarsi (Dunia puuni), bee ti nina n-kuli bi pali ba (bu…£um Ňč…Ē ni)?‚ÄĚ"
  38,64,"Achiika! Di lala bu…£um bihi namgbanpeeni Ňč…Ē maa ny…õla y…õlimaŇčli."
  38,65,"(Yaa nyini Annabi)! YőĶlima! Achiika! Mani ny…õla sa…£isigu lana. Yaha! Duuma jőĶmdigu n-kani ni yőĶlimaŇčli na…£ila Naawuni, O ny…õla za…£iyini, Ny…õŇčda."
  38,66,"‚ÄúSagbana mini tiŇčgbani, n-ti pahi din be di sunsuuni Duuma, Ňäuna n-ny…õ Ny…õŇčda, ChőĶmpaŇčlana."
  38,67,"(Yaa nyini Annabi)! YőĶlima: ‚ÄúDi (Alkur‚Äôaani) ny…õla lahibali din bara.‚ÄĚ"
  38,68,"Yinim‚Äô (Larbunim‚Äô) mi ny…õla ban lebi biri ka ch…õ li."
  38,69,"N-di ka baŇčsim shőĶli n-zaŇč chaŇč Malaaikanim‚Äô sani saha sh…õli b…õ ni daa ŇčmőĶri namgbankpeeni la."
  38,70,"B…õ bi si…£siri wahayi n-tiri ma na m-pahila n-ny…õla sa…£isigulana n-tin ya polo ni."
  38,71,"(Yaa nyini Annabi)! Teemi saha shőĶli a Duuma (Naawuni) ni daa yőĶli Malaaikanima: ‚ÄúAchiika! N (Mani Naawuni) ny…õla Ňäun y…õn nam ninsala ni yőĶ…£ari.‚ÄĚ"
  38,72,"‚ÄúDinzu…£u, N-yi ti nam o naai, ka p…ĒbsiN ny…õvuli niŇč o ni, yi (Malaaikanim‚Äô) man lum ya, ka ny…õla ban niŇčdi suzuuda n- tiri o.‚ÄĚ"
  38,73,"Ka Malaaikanim‚Äô zaasa lu n-niŇč suzuuda n-ti o namgbaniyini."
  38,74,"Na…£ila Ibliisa (shintaŇč) n-daa tibgi o maŇča, ka pahi gutulunim‚Äô puuni."
  38,75,"Ka O (Naawuni) yőĶli: ‚ÄúYaa nyini Ibliisa (shintaŇč)! Bo n-leei m…ĒŇč a ni a lu suzuuda ti N-ni nam ni N (Mani Naawuni) nuhi ayi? Di ni b…ĒŇč…Ē, a tibgila a maŇča, bee a bela ban duhiri b…õ maŇč‚Äô zu…£usaa puuni?"
  38,76,"Ka o (shintaŇč) yőĶli: ‚ÄúMani n-gari o, A nam ma mi ni bu…£um, ka nam o ni yőĶ…£iri.‚ÄĚ"
  38,77,"Ka O (Naawuni) yőĶli: ‚ÄúT…Ē! Yim di (Alizanda maa) puuni, achiika! A ny…õla b…õ ni kari so yihi N namb…Ēz…Ēhigu ni.‚ÄĚ"
  38,78,"‚ÄúYaha! Achiika! N narimbu be a zu…£u n-zaŇč hali ni Sanyoodali.‚ÄĚ"
  38,79,"Ka o (shintaŇč)yőĶli: ‚ÄúYaa n Duuma (Naawuni)! Na…£isim ma hali ni dabsi‚Äô shőĶli Chiyaama ni y…õn ti yi…£isi.‚ÄĚ"
  38,80,"Ka O (Naawuni) yőĶli: ‚ÄúAchiika! A be b…õ ni y…õn na…£isi sh…õba ni.‚ÄĚ"
  38,81,"‚ÄúN-zaŇč chaŇč dabsili sh…õli din mali sahamirili dali.‚ÄĚ"
  38,82,"Ka o (shintaŇč)yőĶli: ‚ÄúM-po A nam ny…õŇčsim, achiika! N-ny…õla Ňčun y…õn birgi ba namgbaniyini.‚ÄĚ"
  38,83,"‚ÄúNa…£ila b…õ puuni ban ny…õ A dabgahinda.‚ÄĚ"